], "Tuesday": ["4 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Wednesday": ["4 a.m.–10 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name": "medium_nice", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFDYo77BGcOj1gVOxIdDtk4K7d8Tmgm8RwulDHbG7MSsWJSIje=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Pickleball Thanh Hà is a great spot for anyone looking to play in a well-maintained and dedicated space. The court is set up nicely, making it a solid choice for both casual players and those who take the game a bit more seriously. One cool touch is their stylish colorful-themed paddle courts.\n\nWith 7 courts they are the biggest in Hoi An. If you’re into pickleball and in the area, it’s definitely worth checking out. It’s a good place to get a game going and be part of the growing pickleball scene in Vietnam!", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Jkcn_Hu_hvbxiVhnNe5R3avmjQzP8JKaA0NuAR1Tyvy7edPOedyC2mKZPW1qy5ljX5MT8g6v-b0jeDfzA8hSd_tdoRyttj4El5o2usWsZM9YIoZRqzvrPWdvrtSn3RhQ9GK6Rrw=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn24cySsMXCz6aYcw9ziffRD2OporM7-BJpIOW9RSy0hCIIZv6zfnz4Le8nEsm_wsMUmrWaaIOHjYwAjKuB5kZCWymHVsKnZJXr9O-IcH1NYZQCsppG3uxlXLzDKgK7LjpqP3otiHA=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn17MVd2GS19eXLSNLGtJ2Ttf9WIod68jaXSmi2AI-w6MqV0afp2wnLb1E1mpNKMVcL8kfiO6rimQXLJlak_UPP9YYqhAnNxBkt6RwuQGada34MsJbqaFC_tlv66aIMhcaoDA9I-=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2ncvSwM_z6N8dQfb-5HwFbV-gTSAwmTVwpH1fI1Y_WqDObZV6gD4kXlf4dEe-062bwS3HshIUPOQgONpgRjaP0qOdnpohcJ65JX2q4e3lLz8KMv7FiBlbXTI4B8ZN7MTPiBD-4gg=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2LzolMXnn5BxPycdpJybkz85B8Zqb-w4j-2skNLiL6uGtiAiO3gImm-sQLUXxw_PNHlg42xRiru-HCIh5er0sy4_OTxKSIgwkLqAyG5GlSQ_9ZaZcZNQeW1CCFQSvNZBKybxPa=k-no"], "When": "2025-3-2"}, {"Name": "Roryandjuliet Douglas", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWD3LCIfOn_X4PhraayQKoKYGcnNSxD0NW8M8qbt99EYXrUT5o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Nice courts, good equipment 😊 Cost 180k for 2 people and hiring 2 racquets for the hour. Was very quiet at 7am when we started, got a bit busier by 8am", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Mattea Käppeli", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOG29jZpEFbRI1ELmoX5b8B27e_VL0MvCxu53CmCjDt1SnBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "such a fun sport and easy to rent a court for an hour!", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Jenny Heavey", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_aTXPU5facDhUqOPyhc3K7Fhh7UpBk2uj80ooTqSf4t68bQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Great place to meet the local Pickleballers. We were welcomed to play on our holiday from Melbourne", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Joe Lum", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwD7Z8C9Rx5z_Kdv63Dea-QoTn6FLbdkh6xMtf9_fkswzsjjCivw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "I''m from the states and was looking for a drop-in Open Play, and just happened to come upon a \"morning crowd\" that gets there at 9:30am (about 8 of them).  They welcomed me in and we had some great competitive games for a couple of hours.  The manager at the front desk doesn''t speak english and thought I wanted an hourly rental.  Good thing one of the players was billingual and it was just 30K for a \"social club fee\" for two hours.  There are 5 courts from what I saw and I don''t know whether or not there''s an afternoon/evening crowd or not, but when I left at 11:30am, no one else was playing.  Water is cheap too.  I''d say it''s a hit or miss, but I was very happy with the games!", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Nguyenquang Minh", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK8k9Mmjwcmi7QAs6HsQ9Z7NcmQFroRRsmeGls1RPqMVd_i-eY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100", "Rating": 1, "Description": "Mình quên cái đai lưng ở đấy,điện cho chủ sân rất nhiều lần,nhưng cố tình trì hoãn.Mình ở HN,đến khi cho người quên qua lấy thì k nghe máy,nhân viên thì bảo k biết. Làm mất công bạn chạy từ Đà nẵng vào. Chán.", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Tri Minh", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbYpmbYarCnxFCRI4mhvRG2v_8UX0Cvb_xqoVSzCyzxcMf3A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Sân pickleball thoáng mát nhất Hội An. Giá rẻ, nên đến đây để trải nghiệm.", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3QyLmALcsrCoiDIOCWAUuSwJbAMh1ExHzDhTnc4AcpdB-Q5P9Hf-cMyc4gLIspj6ooLVOwFr46cLrnffqqbzbhIOPoZ-bxc-LCkdEwgym-ld1oIzUBbFB_r69NhPE907oXdsoAZA=k-no"], "When": "2025-4-3"}, {"Name": "Thuong Tran", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVoxsSrbj4mDWvzKZm6oWiZ3Zauz2rsJIqANapp2XGapvlq5qD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Sân chơi rất ok, sạch sẽ, dịch vụ tốt", "Images": null, "When": ""}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday": {"10": 60, "11": 42, "12": 31, "13": 25, "14": 28, "15": 40, "16": 40, "17": 31, "18": 25, "19": 14, "20": 11, "21": 8, "3": 0, "4": 20, "5": 17, "6": 25, "7": 31, "8": 48, "9": 54}, "Monday": {"10": 54, "11": 37, "12": 31, "13": 37, "14": 37, "15": 42, "16": 40, "17": 42, "18": 34, "19": 40, "20": 40, "21": 48, "3": 0, "4": 5, "5": 11, "6": 20, "7": 40, "8": 54, "9": 60}, "Saturday": {"10": 88, "11": 100, "12": 77, "13": 68, "14": 54, "15": 54, "16": 42, "17": 40, "18": 31, "19": 37, "20": 25, "21": 22, "3": 0, "4": 25, "5": 20, "6": 31, "7": 42, "8": 68, "9": 88}, "Sunday": {"10": 57, "11": 42, "12": 40, "13": 40, "14": 54, "15": 54, "16": 60, "17": 45, "18": 42, "19": 34, "20": 37, "21": 28, "3": 0, "4": 22, "5": 31, "6": 25, "7": 40, "8": 48, "9": 62}, "Thursday": {"10": 25, "11": 22, "12": 20, "13": 31, "14": 54, "15": 65, "16": 60, "17": 51, "18": 48, "19": 37, "20": 37, "21": 34, "3": 0, "4": 17, "5": 14, "6": 17, "7": 20, "8": 22, "9": 25}, "Tuesday": {"10": 45, "11": 31, "12": 20, "13": 17, "14": 28, "15": 31, "16": 42, "17": 40, "18": 45, "19": 37, "20": 31, "21": 34, "3": 0, "4": 17, "5": 17, "6": 22