 and careful to point out what my movements need to be improved.\nI think it is a good opportunity, because I live in Hong Kong and there are not many coaches who are good at singles. This is a good place to learn pickleball by Coach Trung .", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2a_cdbKb7ZJmjemDw0RNGRFqQ6dhWNR4xe4CWsGtMY-DZN5LMHCaSpFPETAGxoA6Z1LMA5WGKfnn3A5R2pUjrk2Bl4MqAXQk_xAczsajbioHwNXC7ckn7qFa0dXtuiGM4nM5EAxDIRAVo=k-no"], "When": "2025-7-16"}, {"Name": "Кирилл Беляков", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfx1ai4xsoWviLuOFXZs3zsCSTkTNnsVYEbQ76LB29R48qhg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Very nice place! I was very glad to play here, will play in the future!", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Lien Nguyen", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWaAF7cGQx-Q4E_DrIIw1YSdwJSxFCGjumpaO9v0YNlccyXtpq4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Sân mát , thoáng\nCụm 2 sân lưới cao nên hạn chế bóng bay qua\nNhân viên thân thiện, nhiệt tình hướng dẫn khách\nSẽ quay lại ủng hộ nhiều lần", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1lW72iURtjLeZPj9csRsj3k36IEJo5umneolirekS6ploCF4JaweI3SLEL-Ma7UjB6l3IKXjyDHmj_72i5PKKpNBuZLb2BGnHlSdRNrS8-SfhMcaABgT89wYVk-SuabqJ92RVekGNYHq64=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0xoPS_7o6_p7-Fkv0Ync_7q_S1BNMWxg1KZRcr3LR_Z7VYt2xGamaEB1VMTsDXLXWXJr8S7Pwlo6R3NqsQOHGCA3hD9indIwlhhZA7Un2UgkqO3YhXZbeVDyldR6P-S1POfmAr1NyIU0bz=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Y3Mg49lzft1h1NEELI05GsSFrGUKgNWbJxVI6kDhWdb80t9dsFimCs7J9KkJqcuv7uR7f61cEIXeE0sRtqNb6J3X-qZhQV0u8aV4wMydLVIdDHaCU1q5U67rigKX8QbQK2o8GWYZc4gY1=k-no"], "When": "2025-9-5"}, {"Name": "Shakhboz Mamatkulov", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL51G2j0-Ta-lo9KxOPxw5TQy-WH_34k80LwNlFmQEqsBSdKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 1, "Description": "Полный мусор. Не разговаривают нормально,лежит и ведет как-то диалог.Про 